WEBVTT

00:00.165 --> 00:01.361
And what's your address?

00:02.618 --> 00:04.124
94 Tindall street.

00:04.413 --> 00:05.493
How do you spell Tindall?

00:06.165 --> 00:08.261
T - I - N - D - A - L - L

00:08.783 --> 00:09.369
Thank you.

00:09.653 --> 00:11.026
And your post code?

00:12.927 --> 00:13.885
Can you repeat that please?

00:13.975 --> 00:16.575
K T 9 8 N B?

00:17.935 --> 00:19.127
And your telephone number?

00:20.218 --> 00:24.141
O 1 3 7 2 8 9 5 3 1

00:25.510 --> 00:26.447
Thank you Ms. Fawcett.

00:26.806 --> 00:27.325
Goodbye.

00:27.653 --> 00:28.313
Hello I'm...

00:28.411 --> 00:31.526
Julia! Welcome to Apex TV.

00:31.953 --> 00:32.604
Come in.

00:32.803 --> 00:33.649
No, don't come in.

00:34.747 --> 00:37.111
This is my personal assistant, Rebecca Bond.

00:37.221 --> 00:38.232
How do you do, Rebecca?

00:38.369 --> 00:39.209
Pleased to meet you.

00:39.523 --> 00:41.385
Come and meet some of the people in the newsroom.

00:41.632 --> 00:42.563
Is Fredrick in?

00:42.777 --> 00:43.956
He's managing director.

00:44.220 --> 00:45.525
No, he's in London.

00:45.990 --> 00:47.870
Oh, I see, right.

00:48.163 --> 00:49.344
Well, come on then, Julia.

